Outlier Treatment¶

In [113]:
def remove_outliers(col):
    lower_limit, upper_limit = df_new1[col].quantile([0.25,0.75])
    IQR = upper_limit - lower_limit
    lower_whisker = lower_limit - 1.5 * IQR
    upper_whisker = upper_limit + 1.5 * IQR
    return np.where(df_new1[col]>upper_whisker,upper_whisker,np.where(df_new1[col]<lower_whisker,lower_whisker,df_new1[col]))
In [114]:
outlier_cols = ['Temperature', 'Weekly_Sales']

Outlier Treatment¶

In [154]:
def remove_outliers(col):
    lower_limit, upper_limit = df_ex3[col].quantile([0.25,0.75])
    IQR = upper_limit - lower_limit
    lower_whisker = lower_limit - 1.5 * IQR
    upper_whisker = upper_limit + 1.5 * IQR
    return np.where(df_ex3[col]>upper_whisker,upper_whisker,np.where(df_ex3[col]<lower_whisker,lower_whisker,df_ex3[col]))
In [155]:
